section.def:
claim
                (申索) means a claim lodged under section
                5(1);

claimant
                (申索人) means a person who has lodged a
            claim;

land
                (土地) means a lot or lots, or part or parts
            thereof;

paragraph.content:
where the land exchange entitlement is granted in consideration of the
                surrender of any land or interest in land to the Government, the surrender of the
                land or interest in land has taken place before the commencement date;

where the land exchange entitlement is granted in consideration of the
                    surrender of any land or interest in land to the Government, the land so
                    surrendered;
